          "character": "关泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位仁兄，黄爷一人前去探山，这般时候，还不见到来，却是为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想黄老兄弟一人前去探山，身无寸铁，十分危险，我等何不迎上前去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、纪全、何路通",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言之有理，大家一同迎上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说着说着，他倒来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位仁兄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、纪全、何路通、朱光祖",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄爷回来了，请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、纪全、何路通、朱光祖",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此番前去，可曾会过那窦尔敦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也曾会过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、纪全、何路通、朱光祖",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有御马的下落"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御马现在他处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何路通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然现在他处，俺何路通倒有一计在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸、关泰、纪全、朱光祖",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何妙计？"
        },
        {
          "character": "何路通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用些干柴烈火，将连环套团团围住，架起火来，将那王八日的烧死在内！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何爷，要照着你这么一办，不必说，是一个也跑不了啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "何路通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是自然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有一件。要把窦尔敦烧死在内，那御马也就烧死在里头了，那时叫黄老兄弟"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎样销差？怎样回复彭大人？这不是鸟枪换炮，越玩越壮啦吗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "何路通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好，全当你靡有说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何路通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就算我靡有说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄贤弟，既然见着了窦尔敦，御马有了下落，这真是万全之幸。但不知那窦尔"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敦盗取御马，到底所为何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是李家店比武的仇恨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，但不知他现在作何打算？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他与我约定明日下山比武，倘若胜不过俺，情愿将御马献上，甘心认罪。俺若"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胜不过他，俺就替父认罪，万死不辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，明日大家还须要小心一二。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明日比试还要仗众位仁兄帮助！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、纪全、何路通、朱光祖",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那个自然，请至后面。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、关泰、纪全、何路通同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀且住，看今日黄老兄弟一人前去探山，身上并无寸铁，可算得是心粗胆壮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "常言道的好：杀一人如同草芥，留一名重如泰山。看黄贤弟，明日在山下同"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他比试，倘若得胜，自是万全之幸，倘若胜不过那窦尔敦，我黄贤弟一世英名，"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂不是付于流水？嗳呀妙吓，看黄贤弟的钢刀现在我手，我不免今晚盗了他"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "的腰牌，私入连环套，探听窦尔敦虚实，明日山下，也好做一准备！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何路通 （内同白） 朱仁兄请来吃酒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就来，就来就来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾就是这个主意！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何路通 （内同白） 朱仁兄，快来吃酒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖下。）"
        }
      ],
