    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二喽啰",
        "朱光祖"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖上，走边。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，朱光祖，时才间盗了黄贤弟的腰牌，不免去到连环套走走。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄龙滚） 为宾朋光侠义英豪，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趁黄昏去走这遭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但只见黄叶飘飘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不觉得来在了这连环套。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖叫门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，开门！"
        },
        {
          "character": "二喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也是连环套里的喽啰，奉了寨主之命，在这山下探听了一桩好买卖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二喽啰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有腰牌？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎的无有。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（石榴花） 尊二位你且稍待，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见寨主要细说明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖、二喽啰同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "朱光祖→二喽啰",
          "turns": 2
