    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "厨子",
        "更夫",
        "朱光祖"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（厨子捧酒肴上，更夫自下场门上，朱光祖随更夫暗上，厨子持盘上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "更夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿奸细！"
        },
        {
          "character": "厨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "更夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是厨子吓。好，你去干你的，我去干我的，他去干他的。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（更夫下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "厨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今晚上寨主爷要喝酒，叫我预备酒菜，不免就此送去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖提厨子帽楹。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "厨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿，靡有风，怎么把帽子会掉啦，这还是漆黑，还得瞎摸。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（厨子放盘子在地，摸帽。朱光祖用迷药入酒壶内，厨子持帽戴。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "厨子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我这儿得啦，他那儿光景也得啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（厨子持盘子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀妙吓，我身边所带八宝勾魂夺魄散许久未用，不料用在今日，真真是巧的"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "很！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "更夫→厨子",
          "turns": 2
