    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "朱光祖",
        "窦尔敦"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦尔敦上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "天霸生来好大胆，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "竟敢一人来探山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "看是谁人来占先。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（厨子持盘上，送桌子上，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将闷奄奄独坐在牛皮大帐，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "准备明日下山岗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦尔敦连斟连饮。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "莫非酒内有埋藏？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦尔敦睡。朱光祖上，推门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦尔敦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦尔敦酣呼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦寨主！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦尔敦酣呼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀妙吓，看窦尔敦现在已是人事不知，我不免将他杀死，以报盗御马之恨！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（番石榴） 俺这里拔出钢刀，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫他性命难逃！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖欲杀，窦尔敦翻身。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀且住，本当将他杀死，念起他是老一辈的英雄，怎肯将他伤害。看他的虎"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头双钩现在墙上，我不免将他的双钩盗去，将黄贤弟的钢刀插在桌案之上。那"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦尔敦醒来，管叫他魂飞胆怕我那黄贤弟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦尔敦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦尔敦睡。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦寨主！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦尔敦睡。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖盗钩。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朱光祖 （番石榴） 盗双钩插上了钢刀，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下山去细说根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖下。窦尔敦醒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只吃得醉醺醺心中烦躁，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又只见桌案山明插钢刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，案上插定钢刀一把，待我看来。漕标副将黄。原来是天霸私自前来。吓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺的虎头双钩哪里去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位英雄走上！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四英雄、四头目同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四英雄、四头目",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寨主何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那天霸夜晚私入寨中，将俺双钩盗去，桌案之上插定钢刀而去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四英雄、四头目",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日比试，还须要格外小心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大家饱餐战饭，一同下山便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦尔敦、四英雄、四头目同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "窦尔敦→朱光祖",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "朱光祖→窦尔敦",
