    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "何路通",
        "关泰",
        "朱光祖",
        "窦尔敦",
        "纪全",
        "黄天霸"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、关泰、何路通、纪全同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朱仁兄哪里去了，因何不见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、何路通、纪全",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等不知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺的钢刀现在他手。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸看腰。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，俺的腰牌不见，莫非被他盗去，有什么歹意不成！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、何路通、纪全",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朱仁兄与我等相交多年，万无歹意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朱光祖其人诡计多端，人心难测，待俺赶上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、何路通、纪全",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朱仁兄回来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朱光祖，你拿我的钢刀，又盗我的腰牌，我且问你，你往哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喝，好大的气头子。我说咱们有话坐下说，好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、何路通、纪全",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大家请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "等我先喘喘气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且讲来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说你今天在山下比试，你准能胜过那窦尔敦么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺若是不胜，情愿替父认罪，万死不辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "话虽如此，只是胜败难定。也是我念你一人前去探山，身无寸铁，可谓心粗胆"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "壮，因此我带了你的钢刀，拿了腰牌，夜入连环套，探听一切，今日大家也好"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "作一准备。不料事逢凑巧，那窦尔敦正要饮酒，是俺身带八宝勾魂夺魄散，于"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他下在酒内，将那窦尔敦灌个人事不知。我本要将他杀死，因念他是前辈的老"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "英雄，不肯伤害他的性命。是我将你的钢刀，与他插在了桌案之上，将他的虎"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头双钩盗来，与你作一他脸儿，也并靡有什么别的意思。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎头双钩现在何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，他在这儿等着我呐。自然是有，这不是虎头双钩嘛！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸看钩。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，纪仁兄，当年在李家店比试，可是此物？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪全",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是此物。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这交朋友，也不过是如此啦罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（纪全推黄天霸赔罪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，朱仁兄，小弟一时莽撞，这厢赔礼了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说如今晚交朋友，真真叫人寒心！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（纪全推黄天霸跪，黄天霸跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟这厢跪下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说你以后这个脾气可是要得改改，别把热心的朋友当作冤家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、何路通、纪全",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大家一同下山去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、何路通、纪全",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手同上，黄天霸、朱光祖、关泰、何路通、纪全、四上手同转场。四下手、四英雄、四头目、窦尔敦"
        },
        {
          "character": "关泰、何路通、纪全",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "同上，同大转场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦寨主请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日你我是怎样比试？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自然英雄对英雄，好汉对好汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，尔等来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老兄呀起开，待我问他几句。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说姓窦的，闻听人言，你善用一对虎头双钩，今天要请你拿出来，我们见识"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见识。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只怕是不在手底下吧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺窦某一十八般兵器件件精通，不用双钩也能擒住尔等！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈，你真是大天白日说瞎话，瞪着两眼不认账。我简直的告诉你说罢，昨晚"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三更时分，黄老兄弟夜入连环套，看你酒醉睡着，本想将你杀死，念在你是前"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辈的老英雄，不肯伤害你的性命，因此将你的虎头双钩带来，将他的刀插在你"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桌案之上。我想他那时候要杀，也就把你给杀啦，我说你一个人有几个脑袋呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姓窦的，你可算真真不懂交情！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李家店里结冤仇，至今怀恨数十秋。插刀盗钩的恩情厚，两下冤仇一笔勾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，将御马牵过来，刑具与俺戴上，一同认罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刑具不戴也罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦尔敦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝廷的王法，焉有不戴之理了，尔等拿过来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大家同至店中一叙，请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖返双钩，头目甲送还钢刀。众人同下。）"
        }
